headline: eBay Celebrates 30 Years of Creating Economic Opportunity for All as it Reinvents the Future of Ecommerce
summary: eBay, Inc. (Nasdaq: EBAY), a global commerce leader that connects millions of buyers and sellers around the world, today celebrates three decades of ecommerce success. Since its founding in 1995, eBay has shaped the way enthusiasts participate in the circular economy, empowering entrepreneurs and creating economic opportunity for millions.
